As a parent or legal guardian, please do not allow minors (under 18 (eighteen) years old) who are under your supervision to provide their personal data to Us. If such personal data is provided to Us, you hereby consent to the processing of the Minorsâ€™ personal data and personally accept and agree to be bound to this Privacy Policy and take responsibility for their actions.
